A 45-year-old Member of County Assembly (MCA) from Kiambu and his girlfriend, 29, have been arrested over murder allegations.  The two are accused of taking part in the killing of a middle-aged man from the county.  Police say the suspects will be produced at the Thika Law Courts later Thursday, May 12.  It is alleged that the ward rep and his lover committed the crime on Tuesday, May 10. This is a developing story, it will be updated with fresh information soon.        By Antony Gitonga | 23 minutes ago By Winfrey Owino | 1 hour ago By Kennedy Gachuhi | 5 hours ago By Paul Ogemba | 12 hours ago